title: Superchick Discography 2001-2013 (11 Releases)
description:
--------------------------------------------------------------
SUPERCHICK DISCOGRAPHY
--------------------------------------------------------------

This discography may or may not be complete.  It contains the following 11 releases...

 * 2001 - Karaoke Superstars
 * 2002 - Last One Picked
 * 2003 - Regeneration
 * 2005 - Beauty From Pain
 * 2006 - Beauty From Pain 1.1
 * 2006 - We Live - Vinyl Promo
 * 2008 - A Film And Television Collection
 * 2008 - Rock What You Got
 * 2009 - Stand In The Rain EP
 * 2010 - Reinvention
 * 2013 - Recollection

Superchick, originally known as Superchic[k], was an American Christian alternative pop/rock band. Their music incorporates various styles such as pop, punk, rock, rap, and R&B. Their sound has been compared to mainstream artists No Doubt and Avril Lavigne with a heavier sound.

Be Blessed,
TorrentTracts - November 2013
